videos.description: Ke'Mon Freeman stiff arms a defender on his way to the end zone to give SMU the lead.
videos.headline: Freeman fights off defenders for TD

videos.description: Cincinnati's Linden Stephens intercepts SMU QB Ben hicks and returns it 18 yards.
videos.headline: Bearcats defense picks off Hicks

videos.description: SMU's Ben Hicks finds his star WR Courtland Sutton for the 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Sutton makes nice grab for TD

videos.description: SMU's star WR Courtland Sutton makes a beautiful catch down the sideline while keeping his feet in bounds.
videos.headline: Sutton makes NFL-like sideline catch

videos.description: Ben Hicks finds Courtland Sutton for the duo's second touchdown connection of the game.
videos.headline: Sutton catches 2nd TD of game

videos.description: Hayden Moore throws a 21-yard strike to Devin Gray to tie the game late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Moore hits Gray to tie game

videos.headline: SMU defense forces turnover to win game in OT
